<section class="flex home">
    <!--Left side of Home-->
    <div class="container flex-vert">
        <!--picture of me-->
        <img class="rounded-circle" src="/img/Me.png" alt="picture of me">
        <!--external icon links-->
        <ul class="list flex">
            <li>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tryston-minsquero/" target="_blank">
                    <img class="out" width="32px" height="32px" src="/img/icons/linkedin.svg" alt="LinkedIn">
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/TrystonMinsquero" target="_blank">
                    <img class="out" width="32px" height="32px" src="/img/icons/github.svg" alt="Github">
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://tryston.itch.io/" target="_blank">
                    <img class="out" width="32px" height="32px" src="/img/icons/itch-io.svg" alt="Itch.io">
                </a>
            </li>         
        </ul>
    </div>
        
    <!--Right side of Home-->
    <div class="container flex-vert" id="about">
        <h2 id="about-header">ABOUT</h2>
        <p id="about-content"> I'm currently a student studying Computer Science at UTD. I plan I graduating Fall of 2022 and I'm looking for internships for the summer. I have a passion for creating which you can see most of my projects from my Github (<a href="https://github.com/TrystonMinsquero">GitHub</a>), this ranges from automating tasks with web scraping in python to simulating different types of schedulers for operating systems in C++. I do have a focus on making games as that's been a lifelong dream, but I'm happy anywhere where I'm making an impact.</p>
    </div>
</section>
        
<div class="projects container">
    <!--Recent Projects-->
    <h3>Recent Projects</h3>
    <section class="flex project-list">
        <ul class="grid list flex">
            {{#each recentProjects}}
                <li>
                    <figure class="hover blue">
                        {{#if this.images.[Cover.png]}}
                            <img src="/{{this.permalink}}/img/Cover.png" alt="{{this.title}}" width="300" height="300">
                        {{else}}
                            <img src="/img/placeholder.png" alt="placeholder" width="300" height="300">
                        {{/if}}
                        <figcaption>
                            <h2>{{this.title}}</h2>
                        </figcaption>
                        <a href="/{{this.permalink}}"></a>
                    </figure>
                </li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>
